description: A man in his 60s is arrested after a woman, believed to be in her 80s, is found dead.
title: Dublin: Elderly woman killed in Clontarf assault
title_page: Dublin: Elderly woman killed in Clontarf assault - BBC News
maintext: The woman, who is believed to be in her 80s, was found dead at a house on Kincora Court, in Clontarf at around 20:00 BST on Sunday.
